data.description: Welcome to this stunning home in a prime Holmen location!This spacious and well-maintained residence boasts 3 to 4 bedrooms and two full bathrooms. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting living space that exudes warmth and charm.The lower level of this home is truly fantastic, featuring a spacious family room that is ideal for gatherings, movie nights, or a kids' play area. With its ample space and versatility, it's a room that can adapt to your family's needs.One of the highlights of this property is the fenced-in backyard, providing both privacy and security for your loved ones. And for those who love outdoor living, you'll adore the maintenance-free deck, perfect for enjoying sunny afternoons or hosting summer barbecues.
